<template><div><h3 id="a-base-tsconfig-for-working-with-node-12" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#a-base-tsconfig-for-working-with-node-12" aria-hidden="true">#</a> A base TSConfig for working with Node 12.</h3>
<p>Add the package to your <code v-pre>&quot;devDependencies&quot;</code>:</p>
<div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> --save-dev @tsconfig/node12
<span class="token function">yarn</span> <span class="token function">add</span> --dev @tsconfig/node12
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Add to your <code v-pre>tsconfig.json</code>:</p>
<div class="language-json ext-json line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-json"><code><span class="token property">"extends"</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"@tsconfig/node12/tsconfig.json"</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><hr>
<p>The <code v-pre>tsconfig.json</code>:</p>
<div class="language-jsonc ext-jsonc line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-jsonc"><code>{
  &quot;$schema&quot;: &quot;https://json.schemastore.org/tsconfig&quot;,
  &quot;display&quot;: &quot;Node 12&quot;,

  &quot;compilerOptions&quot;: {
    &quot;lib&quot;: [&quot;es2019&quot;, &quot;es2020.promise&quot;, &quot;es2020.bigint&quot;, &quot;es2020.string&quot;],
    &quot;module&quot;: &quot;commonjs&quot;,
    &quot;target&quot;: &quot;es2019&quot;,

    &quot;strict&quot;: true,
    &quot;esModuleInterop&quot;: true,
    &quot;skipLibCheck&quot;: true,
    &quot;forceConsistentCasingInFileNames&quot;: true,
    &quot;moduleResolution&quot;: &quot;node&quot;
  }
}

</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>You can find the <a href="https://github.com/tsconfig/bases/blob/master/bases/node12.json" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">code here<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>.</p>
</div></template>
